data.name: Calculation
desc: Specifies how to calculate a value.

items.name: NONE
lines: returns the average of a field.

items.name: AVERAGE
lines: returns the average of a field.

items.name: CORRELATION
lines: returns the correlation of two fields.

items.name: COUNT
lines: counts the number of values, from the field.

items.name: COVARIANCE
lines: returns the measure of the linear relation between paired variables.

items.name: DISTINCTCOUNT
lines: returns the number of none repeating values, from the field.

items.name: MAXIMUM
lines: returns the largest value from the field.

items.name: MEDIAN
lines: returns the middle value in a sequence of numeric values.

items.name: MINIMUM
lines: returns the smallest value from the field.

items.name: MODE
lines: returns the most frequently returning value from the field.

items.name: NTHLARGEST
lines: returns the Nth largest value from the field.

items.name: NTHMOSTFREQUENT
lines: returns the Nth most commonly occurring value from the field.

items.name: NTHSMALLEST
lines: returns the Nth smallest value from the field.

items.name: PERCENTAGE
lines: returns as a percentage of the grand total summary.

items.name: PERCENTILE
lines: returns the value for a specified percentile in a Number or Currency field.

items.name: POPSTANDARDDEVIATION
lines: returns how much each value in the field deviate from the mean or average value for that field.

items.name: POPVARIANCE
lines: returns the square of the standard deviation.

items.name: SAMPLESTANDARDDEVIATION
lines: returns the sample standard deviation for the field.

items.name: SAMPLEVARIANCE
lines: returns the sample variance for the field.

items.name: SUM
lines: returns the total of all the values for the field.

items.name: WEIGHTEDAVG
lines: returns the weighted average for the field.
